                <head>Meeting on Monday</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Generals Wigfall and Smith addressed an unusually large gathering of
                    Augusta citizens at the court house last Monday. These distinguished gentlemen
                    have been in service in the field and in government and offer counsel and wisdom
                    based on their experience. The assembly passed resolutions that the editor hopes
                    will end "extortion and disloyalty in Old Augusta."</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
